= SDL_HINT_VIDEO_ALLOW_SCREENSAVER =
A hint that specifies whether the screensaver is enabled.




== Values ==
{|
|0
|disable screensaver
|-
|1
|enable screensaver
|}

== Default ==
By default SDL will disable the screensaver.


